    height: 16%;
    border: lime double;
    overflow: hidden;
    layer: above;
    offset: 50 20;
    visibility: hidden;
}
```
Change to visible. I have tried it via styles and via the new visible flag. Both have the same behavior: 
```
        self.query_one('#confirm_panel').styles.visibility = 'visible'
